{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:27:05.905Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official Claude documentation and the coordinator-subagent pattern analysis, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Subagents\""},{"type":"text","text":" are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"specialized, isolated worker agents spawned by a main coordinator agent"},{"type":"text","text":" to handle specific tasks, each with their own context window and system prompt, reporting results back to the coordinator."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Subagents are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"focused workers that report back"},{"type":"text","text":" to the main agent — they are spawned by the main agent, have isolated context windows and dedicated system prompts, and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"only report results back to the main agent, never talking to each other"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Basic Flow"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"User Request\n     ↓\nCoordinator Agent\n     ↓\n  Route to specialist\n     ↓\n┌──────────────────────────────────┐\n│ research_agent │ writer_agent │ ← Each: isolated context,\n│ reviewer_agent │ any_specialist │ own system prompt, own tools\n└──────────────────────────────────┘\n     ↓\nTool result back to coordinator\n     ↓\nCoordinator synthesizes → Final output"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Characteristics"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":